CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS airlines AS SELECT
      airline,
      delay,
      time
    FROM 'http://localhost:5173/data/flights.parquet'
    WHERE airline != 'KS' AND airline != '9K'
DESCRIBE SELECT "airline" AS "column" FROM "airlines" AS "source"
DESCRIBE SELECT COUNT(*)::INTEGER AS "column" FROM "airlines" AS "source" GROUP BY ALL
SELECT "airline", AVG("delay") AS "__avg__", COUNT("delay")::INTEGER AS "__n__", STDDEV("delay") AS "__sd__" FROM "airlines" AS "source" WHERE ("time" BETWEEN 6 AND 24) GROUP BY "airline"
SELECT COUNT(*)::INTEGER AS "text", "airline" FROM "airlines" AS "source" WHERE ("time" BETWEEN 6 AND 24) GROUP BY "airline"

CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS mosaic;
